Add `@[elab_as_elim, induction_eliminator, cases_eliminator]` to

- `WithOne.recOneCoe` (added `cases_eliminator`)
- `WithZero.recZeroCoe` (added `cases_eliminator`)
- `ENNReal.recTopCoe`
- `ENat.recTopCoe`
- `EReal.rec`

Mostly cherry-picked from #12605 

Co-authored-by: @negiizhao
